{"day":3,"topic":{"title":"Imperative Sentence","emoji":"⚡","cefr":"A1","difficulty":"beginner","type":"grammar"},"content":{"explanation":"\n**Imperative Sentences — आदेश, अनुरोध, सलाह:**\n\nImperative sentences woh hote hain jo:\n- Command dete hain: \"Sit down!\"\n- Request karte hain: \"Please help me.\"\n- Advice dete hain: \"Drink water daily.\"\n- Warning dete hain: \"Do not touch!\"\n\n**Subject hamesha \"You\" hota hai (lekin bolte nahi)**\n\n🇮🇳 बंद करो दरवाज़ा।\n🇬🇧 Close the door.\n(You = hidden subject)\n  ","rules":["Positive: Base verb से shuru karo — \"Open, Close, Come, Go\"","Polite: Please + base verb — \"Please sit down\"","Negative: Do not / Don't + base verb — \"Don't run\"","Warning: Never + base verb — \"Never lie\"","Suggestion: Let's + base verb — \"Let's go\" (invitation)"],"memoryTrick":"**JUMP!** — Just Use Meaningful Phrase! Imperative = सीधे verb से शुरू। No subject needed.","examples":[{"hindi":"दरवाज़ा खोलो।","english":"Open the door.","type":"Command"},{"hindi":"कृपया बैठ जाइए।","english":"Please have a seat.","type":"Polite"},{"hindi":"शोर मत करो।","english":"Do not make noise.","type":"Negative"},{"hindi":"कभी झूठ मत बोलो।","english":"Never lie.","type":"Warning"},{"hindi":"चलो खाना खाएं।","english":"Let's eat.","type":"Suggestion"},{"hindi":"अपना ख्याल रखो।","english":"Take care of yourself.","type":"Advice"}],"mistakes":[{"wrong":"You open the door.","correct":"Open the door.","why":"Imperative में \"You\" नहीं बोलते"},{"wrong":"Don't to run.","correct":"Don't run.","why":"Don't के बाद 'to' नहीं आता"},{"wrong":"Please to sit.","correct":"Please sit.","why":"Please के बाद 'to' नहीं आता"},{"wrong":"Not go there.","correct":"Don't go there.","why":"Negative में 'Do not / Don't' लगाओ"}],"speakingTips":["Office mein polite imperatives use karo: \"Could you please...?\"","Tone important hai — same words, alag tone = alag meaning!","Emergency mein: short, loud, clear imperatives use karo"]},"vocabulary":[{"id":1,"word":"Command","hindi":"आदेश","ipa":"","example":"\"Stand up!\" is a command."},{"id":2,"word":"Request","hindi":"अनुरोध","ipa":"","example":"\"Please help me.\" is a request."},{"id":3,"word":"Warning","hindi":"चेतावनी","ipa":"","example":"\"Be careful!\" is a warning."},{"id":4,"word":"Instruction","hindi":"निर्देश","ipa":"","example":"Follow the instructions."},{"id":5,"word":"Permit","hindi":"अनुमति देना","ipa":"","example":"You may leave now."},{"id":6,"word":"Forbid","hindi":"मना करना","ipa":"","example":"Smoking is forbidden here."},{"id":7,"word":"Advise","hindi":"सलाह देना","ipa":"","example":"I advise you to rest."},{"id":8,"word":"Polite","hindi":"विनम्र","ipa":"","example":"Always be polite."}],"practice":[{"id":"d03-001","hindi":"यहाँ बैठो।","english":"Sit here.","alternatives":["sit here.","please sit here."],"hint":"Direct command = base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-002","hindi":"कृपया खिड़की बंद करो।","english":"Please close the window.","alternatives":["close the window please."],"hint":"Please + base verb + object","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-003","hindi":"शोर मत करो।","english":"Do not make noise.","alternatives":["don't make noise.","do not be noisy."],"hint":"Don't / Do not + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-004","hindi":"मेरी मदद करो।","english":"Help me.","alternatives":["please help me."],"hint":"Base verb + object","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-005","hindi":"वहाँ मत जाओ।","english":"Do not go there.","alternatives":["don't go there.","do not go there."],"hint":"Don't + verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-006","hindi":"अंदर आ जाओ।","english":"Come inside.","alternatives":["come in.","please come in."],"hint":"Come + direction","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-007","hindi":"अपना काम करो।","english":"Do your work.","alternatives":["do your job.","complete your work."],"hint":"Do + your + noun","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-008","hindi":"ध्यान से सुनो।","english":"Listen carefully.","alternatives":["listen attentively.","please listen carefully."],"hint":"Verb + adverb","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-009","hindi":"देर मत करो।","english":"Do not be late.","alternatives":["don't be late.","do not delay."],"hint":"Don't + be + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-010","hindi":"कृपया धीरे बोलो।","english":"Please speak slowly.","alternatives":["please speak slow."],"hint":"Please + speak + adverb","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-011","hindi":"पानी पियो।","english":"Drink water.","alternatives":["drink some water."],"hint":"Base verb + object","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-012","hindi":"इधर देखो।","english":"Look here.","alternatives":["look over here."],"hint":"Look + direction","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-013","hindi":"झूठ मत बोलो।","english":"Do not lie.","alternatives":["don't lie.","do not tell lies."],"hint":"Don't + verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-014","hindi":"मेहनत से पढ़ो।","english":"Study hard.","alternatives":["study with hard work."],"hint":"Verb + adverb","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-015","hindi":"कृपया मुझे माफ़ करें।","english":"Please forgive me.","alternatives":["please excuse me.","please pardon me."],"hint":"Please + verb + me","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-016","hindi":"दरवाज़ा खोलो।","english":"Open the door.","alternatives":["open the door please."],"hint":"Open + the + noun","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-017","hindi":"मेरे पीछे आओ।","english":"Come after me.","alternatives":["follow me."],"hint":"Come + after me","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-018","hindi":"इस कमरे में मत आओ।","english":"Do not enter this room.","alternatives":["don't come into this room.","do not come in this room."],"hint":"Don't + enter/come into","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-019","hindi":"फ़ोन रख दो।","english":"Keep the phone down.","alternatives":["put the phone down."],"hint":"Put/Keep + object + down","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-020","hindi":"कृपया बैठ जाइए।","english":"Please have a seat.","alternatives":["please sit down.","please be seated."],"hint":"Please have a seat (formal)","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-021","hindi":"जल्दी करो।","english":"Hurry up.","alternatives":["be quick.","please hurry."],"hint":"Hurry up = common phrase","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-022","hindi":"चिंता मत करो।","english":"Do not worry.","alternatives":["don't worry.","stop worrying."],"hint":"Don't worry = common phrase","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-023","hindi":"यहाँ खड़े रहो।","english":"Stand here.","alternatives":["stay here.","remain standing here."],"hint":"Stand/Stay + here","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-024","hindi":"अपना ख्याल रखो।","english":"Take care of yourself.","alternatives":["take care."],"hint":"Take care of + yourself","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-025","hindi":"किसी से झगड़ा मत करो।","english":"Do not fight with anyone.","alternatives":["don't argue with anyone.","do not quarrel with anyone."],"hint":"Don't + fight/argue + with anyone","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-026","hindi":"समय पर आना।","english":"Come on time.","alternatives":["be on time.","arrive on time."],"hint":"Come/Be on time","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-027","hindi":"मुझे बताओ।","english":"Tell me.","alternatives":["let me know.","inform me."],"hint":"Tell + me","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-028","hindi":"खाना खाओ।","english":"Eat your food.","alternatives":["eat food.","have your meal."],"hint":"Eat + your food","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-029","hindi":"तेज़ मत दौड़ो।","english":"Do not run fast.","alternatives":["don't run fast.","do not run so fast."],"hint":"Don't + run","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-030","hindi":"मुझसे झूठ मत बोलो।","english":"Do not lie to me.","alternatives":["don't lie to me.","do not tell me lies."],"hint":"Don't + lie + to me","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-031","hindi":"कृपया अपनी सीट पर बैठें।","english":"Please take your seat.","alternatives":["please sit in your seat."],"hint":"Please + take + your + noun","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-032","hindi":"लाइट बंद कर दो।","english":"Turn off the light.","alternatives":["switch off the light."],"hint":"Turn/Switch off + object","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-033","hindi":"पंखा चालू कर दो।","english":"Turn on the fan.","alternatives":["switch on the fan."],"hint":"Turn/Switch on + object","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-034","hindi":"कृपया इसे दोबारा समझाओ।","english":"Please explain this again.","alternatives":["please explain it again."],"hint":"Please + verb + again","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-035","hindi":"अपने हाथ धो लो।","english":"Wash your hands.","alternatives":["wash your hands please."],"hint":"Wash + your + noun","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-036","hindi":"ज़ोर से मत हँसो।","english":"Do not laugh loudly.","alternatives":["don't laugh loudly."],"hint":"Don't + verb + adverb","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-037","hindi":"सड़क पार करते समय ध्यान रखो।","english":"Be careful while crossing the road.","alternatives":["be careful when crossing the road."],"hint":"Be careful while + verb+ing","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-038","hindi":"कृपया अपना मोबाइल साइलेंट कर दो।","english":"Please put your mobile on silent.","alternatives":["please silence your phone."],"hint":"Please + verb + object","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-039","hindi":"मुझे सच बताओ।","english":"Tell me the truth.","alternatives":["tell me truth."],"hint":"Tell + me + the truth","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-040","hindi":"कमरा साफ़ रखो।","english":"Keep the room clean.","alternatives":["keep your room clean."],"hint":"Keep + object + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-041","hindi":"कृपया कतार में खड़े रहो।","english":"Please stand in the queue.","alternatives":["please stand in line."],"hint":"Stand in + the queue/line","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-042","hindi":"किसी अजनबी पर भरोसा मत करो।","english":"Do not trust a stranger.","alternatives":["don't trust strangers."],"hint":"Don't + trust + noun","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-043","hindi":"अपना होमवर्क समय पर पूरा करो।","english":"Complete your homework on time.","alternatives":["finish your homework on time."],"hint":"Complete/Finish + your + noun + on time","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-044","hindi":"कृपया एक मिनट रुको।","english":"Please wait a minute.","alternatives":["please wait for a minute."],"hint":"Please + wait + a minute","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-045","hindi":"गाड़ी धीरे चलाओ।","english":"Drive the car slowly.","alternatives":["drive slowly."],"hint":"Drive + adverb","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-046","hindi":"खिड़की से बाहर मत देखो।","english":"Do not look outside the window.","alternatives":["don't look out of the window."],"hint":"Don't + look + preposition","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-047","hindi":"सबका सम्मान करो।","english":"Respect everyone.","alternatives":["respect everybody."],"hint":"Respect + everyone","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-048","hindi":"कृपया लाइन में लगें।","english":"Please get in line.","alternatives":["please line up."],"hint":"Get in line / Line up","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-049","hindi":"फ़ालतू बातें मत करो।","english":"Do not talk unnecessarily.","alternatives":["don't talk nonsense.","stop talking unnecessarily."],"hint":"Don't + talk + adverb","explanation":""},{"id":"d03-050","hindi":"हमेशा मुस्कुराते रहो।","english":"Always keep smiling.","alternatives":["always smile."],"hint":"Always + keep + verb+ing","explanation":""}],"mockTest":[{"id":"d03-001-test","hindi":"यहाँ बैठो।","english":"Sit here.","alternatives":["sit here.","please sit here."]},{"id":"d03-002-test","hindi":"कृपया खिड़की बंद करो।","english":"Please close the window.","alternatives":["close the window please."]},{"id":"d03-003-test","hindi":"शोर मत करो।","english":"Do not make noise.","alternatives":["don't make noise.","do not be noisy."]},{"id":"d03-004-test","hindi":"मेरी मदद करो।","english":"Help me.","alternatives":["please help me."]},{"id":"d03-005-test","hindi":"वहाँ मत जाओ।","english":"Do not go there.","alternatives":["don't go there.","do not go there."]},{"id":"d03-006-test","hindi":"अंदर आ जाओ।","english":"Come inside.","alternatives":["come in.","please come in."]},{"id":"d03-007-test","hindi":"अपना काम करो।","english":"Do your work.","alte